adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Kakariko Village...^$3Water Temple...^$4Lake Hylia...^$5The Market...^$6Death Mountain Crater...^$7Kokiri Forest...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to collect&3 Medallions.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be hidden somewhere&%rin Hyrule%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...
